{"type":"message","id":"1af12384","parentId":"71ef5e32","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:35:03.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f0fd33dd93ed44c58bab061a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n2、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n3、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 3.1、满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 3.2、只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n4、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n5、使用openclaw message命令，将数据通过飞书渠道推送给ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5用户；\n6、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773070503445}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1465cb6","parentId":"1af12384","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:35:06.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to read the related files to understand the task better:\n1. get-data-template.md - for the data format\n2. alert-rules.md - for the alert rules\n3. alert-template.md - for the message template\n\nLet me read these files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_edb83dbc6e9e4807a55938ea","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c3a4f5fdb29a4f74b6e45136","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1a03174247d6455690108107","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f527e2ea49164a0f813b144d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773070503446}}
{"type":"message","id":"16133992","parentId":"a1465cb6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:35:06.116Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_edb83dbc6e9e4807a55938ea","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773070506115}}
{"type":"message","id":"97f46d05","parentId":"16133992","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:35:06.119Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c3a4f5fdb29a4f74b6e45136","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n规则条目：\n\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773070506118}}
{"type":"message","id":"28093892","parentId":"97f46d05","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:35:06.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1a03174247d6455690108107","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773070506120}}
