{"type":"message","id":"ee7d230d","parentId":"fb3264b5","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:36:31.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The openclaw CLI doesn't have a --channel option for the message command. Let me check what options are available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_97adaa1277e34bd4bcb2e836","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw message --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773070589985}}
{"type":"message","id":"36df71e6","parentId":"ee7d230d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:36:33.226Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_97adaa1277e34bd4bcb2e836","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.7 (42a1394) — Your .zshrc wishes it could do what I do.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions\n  permissions  Fetch channel permissions\n  pin          Pin a message\n  pins         List pinned messages\n  poll         Send a poll\n  react        Add or remove a reaction\n  reactions    List reactions on a message\n  read         Read recent messages\n  role         Role actions\n  search       Search Discord messages\n  send         Send a message\n  sticker      Sticker actions\n  thread       Thread actions\n  timeout      Timeout a member\n  unpin        Unpin a message\n  voice        Voice actions\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw message send --target +15555550123 --message \"Hi\"\n    Send a text message.\n  openclaw message send --target +15555550123 --message \"Hi\" --media photo.jpg\n    Send a message with media.\n  openclaw message poll --channel discord --target channel:123 --poll-question \"Snack?\" --poll-option Pizza --poll-option Sushi\n    Create a Discord poll.\n  openclaw message react --channel discord --target 123 --message-id 456 --emoji \"✅\"\n    React to a message.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/message"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1677,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.7 (42a1394) — Your .zshrc wishes it could do what I do.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions\n  permissions  Fetch channel permissions\n  pin          Pin a message\n  pins         List pinned messages\n  poll         Send a poll\n  react        Add or remove a reaction\n  reactions    List reactions on a message\n  read         Read recent messages\n  role         Role actions\n  search       Search Discord messages\n  send         Send a message\n  sticker      Sticker actions\n  thread       Thread actions\n  timeout      Timeout a member\n  unpin        Unpin a message\n  voice        Voice actions\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw message send --target +15555550123 --message \"Hi\"\n    Send a text message.\n  openclaw message send --target +15555550123 --message \"Hi\" --media photo.jpg\n    Send a message with media.\n  openclaw message poll --channel discord --target channel:123 --poll-question \"Snack?\" --poll-option Pizza --poll-option Sushi\n    Create a Discord poll.\n  openclaw message react --channel discord --target 123 --message-id 456 --emoji \"✅\"\n    React to a message.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/message","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773070593225}}
